Oaktree Opportunities Fund X, L.P.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 1:17 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Oaktree Opportunities Fund X, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Oaktree Opportunities Fund X, L.P. specializes in distressed-debt and turnaround investments. The fund seeks to invest in shipping, corporate debt, power plants, real estate, specialty finance, retail, and coal sectors. It has a global focus and typically invests in United States, Europe, and emerging markets. The fund seeks to take non-control positions. It consists of a parallel fund Oaktree Opportunities fund Xb.


333 South Grand Avenue28th FloorLos Angeles, CA 90071United StatesFounded in 2014



